# mhyprot.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png)  ![:inline](/images/elmo.gif) 

### Description

mhyprot.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: 9f8f2324-d867-4211-842a-122b93946445
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/khulnasoft-lab/mitigate-drivers/raw/main/drivers/8b779fe1d71839ad361226f66f1b3fe5.bin" "Download" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create mhyprot.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\mhyprot.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start mhyprot.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
